================================================================================
PARODY DECLARATION
================================================================================

Opuncleh is a parody AI agent forked from OpenClaw (https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw).

This project exists for humor, educational purposes, and to demonstrate the art
of intentionally misspelled phonetic English in AI systems. It is not affiliated
with, endorsed by, or connected to the OpenClaw project or its maintainers.

All modifications transform the original work into a comedic derivative that
speaks in "derpy" vocabulary - intentionally misspelled words that phonetically
approximate their correct counterparts.

MODIFICATIONS MADE:
- Global rename: OpenClaw → Opuncleh, Clawd → Lobstr, Molty → Derpy
- Added src/derpy/ module with 966+ word substitutions
- Integrated derpy transform into reply pipeline
- All output text now goes through derpy vocabulary transformation

EXAMPLE TRANSFORMATIONS:
- "The function works correctly" → "Teh funktion werks correktly"
- "Hello friend, how are you?" → "Henlo fren, hao r u?"
- "This is a deep learning model" → "Dis iz a derp lurning modul"

